casebody.data:
Patrick BARILE, on Behalf of Himself and Those Similarly Situated, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
GF-PASSAIC FOODS, LLC, and GF-East Patterson Foods, LLC, Defendants-Respondents. C-522 September Term 2018
081842 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 25, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004706-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
